================================================================================

Y4 is the Type-1 host hypervisor designed to run WaveTensor accelerator
boards across all commercial form factors (server-farm host A,
special-purpose laptop, rack-mount node, handheld+dock unit, embedded
SoC/SoM). Architecture rationale, base-OS reuse policy, IPC and allocator
fusion model, formal-verification stance, and bootloader selection are
documented in `docs/architecture.md` (canonical) and were originally drafted
under the WaveTensor project as `host_a_custom_hypervisor.md`.

